  49. ‌Caml_inline int caml_addrmap_iter_ok(struct addrmap* t, addrmap_iterator i)

  59. ‌Caml_inline addrmap_iterator caml_addrmap_next(struct addrmap* t,
  60.                                                addrmap_iterator i)
  61. {
  62.   if (!t->entries) return (uintnat)(-1);
  63.   i++;
  64.   while (i < t->size && t->entries[i].key == ADDRMAP_INVALID_KEY) {
  65.     i++;
  66.   }
  67.   caml_addrmap_iter_ok(t, i); /* just for assert-checks */
  68.   return i;
  69. }
